%% ═══ L1: Exam Domain Ontology ═══

:: entity id=ent:csat type=System labels.en="CSAT English" labels.ko="수능 영어"
@aliases: ["수능특강", "수능완성", "College Scholastic Ability Test"]
The standardized Korean college entrance English exam testing reading comprehension,
grammar, vocabulary, and logical reasoning across 45 questions in 70 minutes.
::

:: entity id=ent:passage type=Concept labels.en="Reading Passage" labels.ko="독해 지문"
@aliases: ["text", "지문", "reading text"]
The core content unit of a CSAT English question — a 150-300 word English paragraph
that students must analyze for meaning, structure, and linguistic features.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-topic type=Concept labels.en="Topic Inference" labels.ko="글의 주제"
@aliases: ["주제 추론", "main topic"]
@category_id: "cat_01"
Identify the central topic or thesis of the passage.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-implication type=Concept labels.en="Implication Inference" labels.ko="함축 의미 추론"
@aliases: ["함의추론", "implied meaning"]
@category_id: "cat_02"
Infer the implied or deeper meaning beyond the literal text.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-grammar type=Concept labels.en="Grammar Judgment" labels.ko="어법"
@aliases: ["어법 판단", "grammaticality"]
@category_id: "cat_03"
Judge grammatical correctness of underlined expressions in context.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-vocabulary type=Concept labels.en="Vocabulary" labels.ko="어휘"
@aliases: ["어휘 적절성", "word choice"]
@category_id: "cat_04"
Select the contextually appropriate vocabulary item.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-blank type=Concept labels.en="Blank Completion" labels.ko="빈칸 추론"
@aliases: ["빈칸 완성", "fill-in-the-blank"]
@category_id: "cat_05"
Complete the blank with the most logically fitting phrase or sentence.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-order type=Concept labels.en="Sentence Ordering" labels.ko="글의 순서"
@aliases: ["순서 맞추기", "text ordering"]
@category_id: "cat_07"
Arrange given paragraphs in the correct logical order.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-insertion type=Concept labels.en="Sentence Insertion" labels.ko="문장 삽입"
@aliases: ["문장 넣기", "insert sentence"]
@category_id: "cat_08"
Determine the correct position for a given sentence within the passage.
::

:: entity id=ent:question-type-summary type=Concept labels.en="Summary Completion" labels.ko="요약문 완성"
@aliases: ["요약", "summarize"]
@category_id: "cat_09"
Complete a summary statement with appropriate paired words.
::

:: entity id=ent:worksheet type=Concept labels.en="Worksheet" labels.ko="워크시트"
@aliases: ["학습지", "활동지"]
Published output format: student worksheet or teacher guide.
::

:: entity id=ent:teacher-guide type=Concept labels.en="Teacher Guide" labels.ko="교사용 참고서"
@aliases: ["교안", "수업 가이드"]
Detailed analysis document for instructors with scaffolding strategies.
::

